kills  your  cat  (etc.)  either due to programming bugs or improper
usage, it's not my problem.

You  are  encouraged  to copy the demo version freely as long as you
include  all  the files that came with the distribution archive.  To
order  the  real version or to send comments, complaints etc.  write
to  @{"  Laserdance  Productions  "  link  contact}.   Thank  you in
advance.

